<section
  id="video"
  data-section="video"
  class="relative z-20 w-full bg-ink py-32 text-paper md:py-48"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-6">

    <div class="mb-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-7">
        <p class="eyebrow mb-6 text-paper/40" data-i18n="t">
          <span data-lang="es">En acción</span>
          <span data-lang="en" class="hidden">In action</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="h-display text-[clamp(2.25rem,5vw,4.5rem)] leading-[0.95]" data-i18n="t">
          <span data-lang="es">Míralo <span class="text-pop">construirse</span>.</span>
          <span data-lang="en" class="hidden">Watch it <span class="text-pop">being built</span>.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="md:col-span-5 md:pt-2 text-paper/55 md:text-lg" data-i18n="t">
        <span data-lang="es">De la lámina al techo en días. Sin soldadura, sin maquinaria pesada — solo comunidad, un taladro y remaches POP.</span>
        <span data-lang="en" class="hidden">From sheet metal to roof in days. No welding, no heavy machinery — just community, a drill, and POP rivets.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative w-full overflow-hidden" style="padding-top: 56.25%;">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0nvnQnBt1Hw?rel=0&modestbranding=1"
        title="Lamina POP — construcción en acción"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
        loading="lazy"
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full border-0"
      ></iframe>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
